1. find all html tags in string
/<((?=!\-\-)!\-\-[\s\S]*\-\-|((?=\?)\?[\s\S]*\?|((?=\/)\/[^.\-\d][^\/\]'"[!#$%&()*+,;<=>?@^`{|}~ ]*|[^.\-\d][^\/\]'"[!#$%&()*+,;<=>?@^`{|}~ ]*(?:\s[^.\-\d][^\/\]'"[!#$%&()*+,;<=>?@^`{|}~ ]*(?:=(?:"[^"]*"|'[^']*'|[^'"<\s]*))?)*)\s?\/?))>/ig

2. Find javascript tags

3.Html tag finder(smaller and less powerfull)--it will not detect space i.e < b> 
</?\w+((\s+\w+(\s*=\s*(?:".*?"|'.*?'|[\^'">\s]+))?)+\s*|\s*)/?>
